<br>
Two speeding, but got let off with a warning.<br>
Three speeding, got tickets.<br>
One tailgating, got a ticket (it was an older couple doin 50 in the left lane on the highway, in case ya were wondering).<br>
<br>
Took all the tickets to court.<br>
<br>
Plea-bargained three down to half points &amp; fines.<br>
<br>
Plea-bargained one down to half points, and judge dropped the fines because I had to wait so long, and the cop who wrote the ticket was a jerk (judge was like &quot;It says here on your ticket you weren't happy about receiving the ticket&quot;, and I was like &quot;Not really&quot;, and the judge was like &quot;I wouldn't be either.&quot; and kinda smirked at the ticket like WTF kind of comment is that to put on a ticket?).<br>
<br>
